ithu nammude katha ( malayalam : ഇതു നമ മുടെ കഥ , english : this is our story ) is a 2011 malayalam film written and directed by rajesh kannankara , who debuts with this film .   it stars asif ali , nishan , abhishek , vineeth kumar , ananya , amala paul and nimisha in the lead roles .   the film is a remake of 2009 tamil film nadodigal with story credited to samuthirakani .   the story revolves around a girl with lot of problems .   she enters the life of a group of three youngsters .   the film released on 28 january 2011 , but was a flop at the box office , mainly due to poor publicity .